    Embed time series

    embed_reg.Rd

    Embed time series

    embed_reg(
  x,
  y,
  lags = 1,
  encoding = c("None", "model_matrix", "target_based"),
  testing = FALSE
)

    Arguments

    model_matrix

    Examples

    
x <- 1:10
set.seed(2020)
df <- data.frame(x1 = x,
                 x2 = c("a", "b", "c", "b", "a",
                        "a", "a", "c", "b", "c"),
                 x3=sort(rnorm(10)))
df$x2 <- as.factor(df$x2)

lags <- 3L

cat("1 - data -----")
#> 1 - data -----
cat("\n")
#> 
print(df)
#>    x1 x2         x3
#> 1   1  a -2.7965343
#> 2   2  b -1.1304059
#> 3   3  c -1.0980232
#> 4   4  b -0.2293777
#> 5   5  a  0.1173668
#> 6   6  a  0.3015484
#> 7   7  a  0.3769721
#> 8   8  c  0.7205735
#> 9   9  b  0.9391210
#> 10 10  c  1.7591313
cat("\n")
#> 

cat("2 - training (model_matrix==FALSE) -----")
#> 2 - training (model_matrix==FALSE) -----
cat("\n")
#> 
cat("\n")

print(after::embed_reg(y=df$x1, x=df[, c("x2", "x3")],
                       lags = lags))
